
# Python & Jupyter
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*.ipynb_checkpoints

# Project Data Outputs (Timestamped Folders)
**/202[0-9]-*
**/202[0-9]_*
**/Run_202[0-9]-*

# Result & Output Folders (Ignore everything inside)
**/Angepasste_Datenbanken/
**/MiniSom_Results/
**/IntraSom_Results/
